  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The goal is to improve the quality of education in Dadaab through a multi-faceted approach, leading to sustainable improvements in refugee education in the camps and beyond. AVSI will also continue supporting female pre-primary teachers&#x2019; professional training with portable cross border recognized documents. AVSI will provide upgraded in-service training for the refugee teachers to keep them abreast with curriculum changes and to address training gaps. AVSI will provide responsive educational and life skills building opportunities for youth.</narrative>
